# .dockerignore — Credit Card Fraud Detection API
# This Dockerfile is used to build the live HF Spaces deployment, where
# model/ IS present and committed. If you clone this GitHub repo to build
# the image yourself, you'll need to add model/ locally first (see README —
# "To retrain the model") since model/ is gitignored here.
#
# Source: https://docs.docker.com/build/concepts/context/#dockerignore-files

# ── Training data (never goes in the image) ───────────────────────────────────
*.csv
*.parquet
*.feather

# ── Jupyter notebooks and checkpoints ────────────────────────────────────────
*.ipynb
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ── Python cache ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/

# ── Test and training scripts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
tests/
SAVE_MODEL_CELL.py
generate_fixtures.py
requirements-notebook.txt

# ── Dev and CI files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.gitignore
.git/
*.md

# ── IDE and OS files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Virtual environments ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
venv/
.venv/
env/
